The paper deals with the problem of computing the number of distinct elements in a data stream, which is a fundamental problem in data structures (cs.DS) and information theory (cs.IT). The paper also discusses the use of interactive protocols, which is a topic in computational complexity (cs.CC) and cryptography (cs.CR).
